<div className="quote" style={{width: "50%"}}>
<h3><b><i>&nbsp;&ldquo;</i></b><span style="font-weight: 400;">For I know the plans&nbsp;I have for you,&rdquo; declares the&nbsp;Lord, &ldquo;plans to prosper&nbsp;you and not to harm you, plans to give you hope and a future.&nbsp;</span><b>12&nbsp;</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">Then you will call&nbsp;on me and come and pray&nbsp;to me, and I will listen&nbsp;to you.&nbsp;</span><b>13&nbsp;</b><span style="font-weight: 400;">You will seek&nbsp;me and find me when you seek me with all your heart.&rdquo;</span></h3>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">--Jeremiah 29:11-13&nbsp;</span></h3>
